{"article_id":"2oui5gjiUEugPAfI","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump has denied","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"money","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"used","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"to buy a porn star 's silence","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"came from election campaign funds .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"He admitted , in a series of tweets ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"that lawyer Michael Cohen had paid off Stormy Daniels during the campaign","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"and that he was reimbursed .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"It was the first time","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"the president has referred directly to the payment ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"although he remains adamant","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"there was no affair with Ms Daniels .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Use of campaign funds would be a violation of federal law .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"Earlier , his legal aide Rudy Giuliani had said","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"the money was Mr Trump 's personal cash .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"The president fired off three tweets on Thursday morning ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"focusing on the reimbursement and a non-disclosure agreement","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"( NDA )","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"with Daniels .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Mr Trump 's argument appears to be that the NDA was a typical agreement","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"entered into by celebrities","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"and therefore not an election-related matter .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"This could be crucial","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"in determining","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"whether the $ 130,000","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"( £95,650 )","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"paid to Ms Daniels","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"was legal .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"The actress says","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"she had an affair with Mr Trump in 2006","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"and she slept with him once .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"In a particularly feisty White House daily news conference on Thursday , press secretary Sarah Sanders was asked","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"when she became aware","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that Mr Trump had repaid Mr Cohen the money .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"`` The first awareness","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"I had","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"was during the","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"[ Giuliani ]","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"interview last night , ''","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"When asked by reporters a month ago","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"if he knew about the payment to Ms Daniels ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Mr Trump said :","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"`` No . ''","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"When asked why the payment was given to Ms Daniels ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"he added :","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"`` You 'll have to ask Michael Cohen . ''","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Speaking on Fox TV last week ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Mr Trump suggested some knowledge of the matter","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"in admitting","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Mr Cohen had represented him during the `` crazy Stormy Daniels deal '' ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"but he did not go into specifics .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Mr Cohen , for his part , told the New York Times in February :","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"`` Neither the Trump Organization nor the Trump campaign was a party to the transaction with Ms Clifford ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"and neither reimbursed me for the payment , either directly or indirectly . ''","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"How this relates to any alleged personal repayments by Mr Trump is unclear .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"Mr Cohen is facing a criminal investigation .","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"FBI agents searched his home and office in New York recently in relation to the NDA .","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"Donald Trump 's April assertion","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"that he had no idea","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"where Michael Cohen found the money","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"to secure Stormy Daniels ' silence","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"seems ,","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"to borrow a phrase from Nixon administration press secretary Ron Ziegler ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"`` no longer operative '' .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"White House Press Secretary Sarah Huckabee Sanders stated in March","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"that the president had `` no knowledge of any payments '' .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"Now she 's saying","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"she ca n't comment on the situation .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"Michael Cohen","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"-","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"before he cited the Fifth Amendment in court","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"to avoid self-incriminating testimony -","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"insisted","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"that he made the Daniels payment out of his own pocket .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"Former New York Mayor Rudy Giuliani , a new arrival on the president 's personal legal team , says","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Mr Trump reimbursed Mr Cohen for the payment over the course of 2017","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"and was tasked with handling `` things like this '' .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"Someone has lied or is lying","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"to protect Donald Trump .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"The questions are who - and why .","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"Michael Avenatti , Daniels ' lawyer , says","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"his client has evidence","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"that will prove the veracity of their claims .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"Mr Trump , in his tweets , promises a lawsuit","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"to enforce Daniels ' silence","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"about what he calls `` false and extortionist accusations '' .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"This White House storm shows no signs of ending anytime soon .","depth":2},{"id":88,"text":"US federal law restricts","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"how much individuals and organisations can contribute to campaign financing ,","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"and there are also strict regulations on the disclosure of the financing .","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"The key question may be whether the money was used","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"to prevent Mr Trump 's reputation being harmed during the campaign ,","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"and therefore be deemed as related to the election .","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"Legal expert Lawrence Noble told the Washington Post :","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"`` If the purpose of this was to stop [ Daniels ] from hurting the campaign ,","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"then what you have is Cohen made a loan to the campaign . ''","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"The $ 130,000 would exceed the amount","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"an individual can donate to a presidential campaign .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"Any repayment by the Trump campaign would violate the law .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"But presidential candidates are allowed to contribute an unlimited amount to their own campaign .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Mr Trump may be arguing","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"that the personal nature of the repayment makes it legal .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"If the $ 130,000 were deemed to have been a loan to Mr Cohen ,","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"the president would only have had to disclose the repayment to the Federal Election Commission","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"if it were an election-related expense .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"There is no mention of any debt to Mr Cohen on Mr Trump 's personal financial disclosure form from June 2017 .","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"Former New York City mayor Rudy Giuliani recently joined Mr Trump 's legal team","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"and had earlier been interviewed by Sean Hannity on Fox News ,","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"surprising many with his comments .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"He was the first","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"to say","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"Mr Trump repaid the money .","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"He added","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"that the president `` did n't know about the specifics of it ,","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"as far as I know ,","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"but he did know about the general arrangement","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"that Michael would take care of things like this '' .","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"Mr Giuliani later spoke to the New York Times ,","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"saying :","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"`` Some time","depth":16},{"id":121,"text":"after the campaign is over ,","depth":16},{"id":122,"text":"they set up a reimbursement , $ 35,000 a month , out of his personal family account . ''","depth":15},{"id":123,"text":"The sum","depth":15},{"id":124,"text":"paid","depth":15},{"id":125,"text":"was $ 460,000- $ 470,000 ,","depth":15},{"id":126,"text":"including expenses ,","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"he said .","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"He also said","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"Mr Trump was aware of what he was going to say on Fox News","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"and that he had spoken to the president before and after the interview .","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"Mr Trump 's tweet also speaks of a monthly retainer ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"although it is unclear about the timing of its payment to Mr Cohen .","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"Mr Giuliani told the Times","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"he did not know","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"whether Mr Trump was aware of the payment to Ms Daniels at the time","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"but his understanding was","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"that the president had only learned about it recently .","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"It is unclear how this fits with Mr Trump 's statement","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"that repayments were made over several months .","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"How did the payment come about","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"and what has happened since ?","depth":7},{"id":142,"text":"After initially denying the payment ,","depth":7},{"id":143,"text":"Mr Cohen eventually admitted","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"he had paid the sum privately to Ms Daniels , real name Stephanie Clifford , in October 2016 out of his own funds in exchange for her silence in a non-disclosure agreement .","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"He says","depth":7},{"id":146,"text":"Mr Trump was not a party to the transaction .","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"In March this year , Ms Daniels filed a lawsuit against the president ,","depth":6},{"id":148,"text":"alleging","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"that the agreement was invalid","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"because Mr Trump did not sign it .","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"While Mr Trump has denied her claims ,","depth":7},{"id":152,"text":"his lawyers are seeking $ 20m in damages from Ms Daniels ,","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"arguing","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"she broke the non-disclosure deal .","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"Ms Daniels is also suing the president over a `` defamatory '' tweet","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"he posted","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"after she said","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"she was threatened by a man in a Las Vegas car park to drop her allegations of the affair .","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"Mr Trump had said","depth":8},{"id":160,"text":"her claims were `` a total con job '' .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":321,"left":247,"right":320,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":247,"left":191,"right":246,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":175,"right":190,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":173,"right":174,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":165,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":0,"right":164,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":